Usage: save_abstract [-help] [-PGpinLayers <layerNameList>] [-cutObs]
                     [-cutObsMinSpacing] [-extractBlockObs]
                     [-extractBlockPGPinLayers <layerNameList>] [-lib <lib>]
                     [-specifyTopLayer <topLayerName>]
                     [-stripePin {top all none}] [-view <view>]

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
-PGpinLayers <layerNameList>             # Specifies list of layers
                                         # (string, optional)
-cutObs                                  # (bool, optional)
-cutObsMinSpacing                        # (bool, optional)
-extractBlockObs                         # (bool, optional)
-extractBlockPGPinLayers <layerNameList>
                                         # Specifies list of layers (string, optional)
-lib <lib>                               # Specifies the target library name,
                                         # default: design lib (string, optional)
-specifyTopLayer <topLayerName>          # top layer name (string, optional)
-stripePin {top all none}                # (enum, optional)
-view <view>                             # Specifies the target view name,
                                         # default: abstract (string, optional)